==Translingual==

===Pronunciation===
/ i / short close front unrounded vowel: as i in bit.  Also / ɪ / near-close near-front unrounded vowel.

===Letter===
'''इ'''

# A vowel of the [[Devanagari]] script.  It's [[matra]], used to modify the inherent vowel in a consonant is written &#x093F;.  For example the first consonant क with the matra looks like: कि.  The matra should appear before the consonant it modifies, though it is pronounced after.

